        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Received her letter of April 24. Has sent her several letters on matters of business.
                Wishes for her to send him items of clothing if Col. {Jeremiah} Wadsworth is sending
                a wagon to the Army. Has heard of the Jays' arriv al from Maj. Benjamin Talmadge.
                Tells of Sam uel Allyn's death in Hampton {Va.} Will writ e to her brother at
                Charleston. Expects next to go to New York. </p>
        </scopecontent>
